title: VA - FAX Compilation II (1995) {Ambient} [FLAC]
description:
Review by John Bush

The second Fax collection is another two-disc set, this time with tracks by Solitaire, Otras 2, Bedroom and Xjacks, not quite the most high-profile acts on the label, though the ubiquitous Namlook does appear on several tracks...


CD 1 Tracklist:
01. Electro Harmonix - Floating Sync (written by Tetsu Inoue & Jonah Sharp)
02. Namlook - The Gate To The Milky Way - excerpt (written by Pete Namlook)
03. Otras 2 - Astralbohrer (written by David Reeves)
04. Recurring Dreams of the Urban Myth - Loop 6 - excerpt (written by Chris Meloche)
05. A Day in the Park - Talk (written by Dr. Atmo, Pino and Wildjamin)
06. Bedroom - Antarctica (written by Daniel Pemberton)
07. Aerial Service Area - Another Green Airport (written by Victor Sol, Nico Heyduck and Atom Heart)

Total time: 01:13:55

CD 2 Tracklist:
01. Music for Ballet - Electro Clips - excerpt (written by Pete Namlook)
02. Transonic - Whirlpool (Slow Spiral Of Clouds) - excerpt (written by Robert Musso)
03. Solitaire - In/Out (written by David Moufang)
04. XJacks - Celophane (written by Dandy Jack and Victor Sol)
05. Wechselspannung - excerpt (written by Jonah Sharp & Pete Namlook)
06. Organic Cloud - Chill In Chill Out (written by Tetsu Inoue)
07. Namlook - Subharmonic Interference - excerpt (written by Pete Namlook)

Total time: 01:12:20
